title: adidas Skateboarding Diagonal Pt. 08 Julien Bachelier
description:
adidas Skateboarding presents the full length European Team video, Diagonal, released in May 2009. Featuring Chewy Cannon, Raul Navarro, Marcos Gomez, Sebastien Daurel, Julien Bachelier, Jeremy Reinhard, Petr Horvat and Gunes Ozdogan with guest appearances by Dennis Busenitz, Lem Villemin, Mark Gonzales, Silas Baxter-Neal, Tim O'Connor, Benny Fairfax, Dave Bachinsky, Nestor Judkins and Vince del Valle. 
Official Website: http://www.adidas.com/skateboarding 
Store Locator: http://bit.ly/qIFMfO
